Scarier is a lazy AI C++ clone of SCARE, Simon Baldwin's C clone of jAsea, Mark J. Tilford's Java GPL clone of the Adrift 4 Runner, combined with a lazy AI C++ clone of the Adrift 5 runner and a lazy AI C++ clone of FrankenDrift, a C# frontend for Adrift 5 by Adrian Welcker.

The Scarier source code is released under the GPL.